  "summary": "Malicious code in amplitude-ma-ts (npm)",
  "details": "Combosquat of the Amplitude analytics package. Both v1.0.22 and v1.0.24 ship an identical postinstall script (Folder/bin/S.js) that collects the hostname, USER, cwd, public IP (via api[.]ipify[.]org using curl), and the contents of /etc/hosts, then exfiltrates all of it as a JSON embed via POST to a Discord webhook (discord[.]com/api/webhooks/1497047226428690432/...). Plain-text data theft via lifecycle hook with no obfuscation.",
